Miscellaneous Highlights: The Proteas face bogey team the Netherlands in their next match at the T20 World Cup on Saturday at New York’s Nassau Stadium.
Others: The ICC Men’s T20 World Cup 2024 in USA and West Indies got underway on 1 June.

A total of three venues in the USA and six in the Caribbean will be used for the ICC Men’s T20 World Cup 2024 after the groups and fixtures for the ninth edition of the 20-over showcase were confirmed.
